      • stream

        public java.util.stream.Stream<java.lang.Object> stream(java.lang.Object root,
                                                        java.util.function.Predicate<java.lang.Object> filter)
        Return a stream of all objects that are reachable from a given object
        Parameters:
        root - - The object to start from
        filter - - A filter to control which objects are traversed. If this filter returns false, that object will not be returned in the stream, and it's references will not be followed.
        Returns:
        A Stream of reachable objects
